<F P=102>  LD0802115094 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 
1100 GMT 8 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0802115094 </F>
<F P=104>  Zagreb Radio Croatia Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Josko Krizelj report from Livno] </F>
  [Excerpt] I have decided to place my mandate as president 
of the Croat republic of Herceg-Bosna at the disposal of this 
assembly until further notice. A presidential council will 
assume the duties of president and will appoint an acting 
president. Mate Boban said this at the end of his introductory 
speech at an extraordinary session of the Chamber of Deputies of 
Herceg-Bosna's Assembly. I will stay with you, Boban said, 
ending his speech. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

