Serbo-Croatian 1329 GMT 7 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0702184894 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Belgrade, 7 Feb (TANJUG) -- The constitutive session 
of the new composition of the assembly [parliament] of the 
