<H3> <TI>   FONET News Agency Begins Operations </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU0802144294 Belgrade NEDELJNA BORBA in Serbo-Croatian 5-6 
February p 5 </F>

<F P=103> AU0802144294 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade NEDELJNA BORBA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Serbo-Croatian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "FoNet News Agency Founded"] </F>
  [Text] A professional and commercial news agency, FONET, 
whose sole founders and owners are journalists Nebojsa Magdeski 
and Zoran V. Sekulic, will commence operations on Monday, 7 
February. The news agency's products will initially consist of 
mainly telephone (audio) reports from correspondents and 
contributors in the country and abroad, which will be offered to 
the electronic media, radio and television. The agency's 
network of correspondents will cover all the main centers in the 
Federal Republic of Yugoslavia, all the most important places on 
the territory of the former Yugoslavia, and a large number of 
places in all the continents. 

</TEXT>

