<F P=100> POLAND </F>
<H3> <TI>   Walesa Countersigns Borowski's Resignation </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0802194894 Warsaw PAP in Polish 1832 GMT 8 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0802194894 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw PAP </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Polish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Warsaw, 8 Feb--President Lech Walesa today 
countersigned the resignation of Marek Borowski, the deputy 
prime minister and finance minister, Ewa Wachowicz, the prime 
minister's press secretary has reported. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS3-30811 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreeu027_p_94006" </HT>


