<H3> <TI>   Borowski To Remain in Post Until Released </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0902130094 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network in Polish 1105 
GMT 9 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0902130094 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Polish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] I shall continue in my post until I am released in 
writing by the president in accordance with the Constitution, 
Marek Borowski said today in an interview for the Polish Radio 
Third Program. 
  [Begin Borowski recording] My resignation is final. The 
objective of the meeting of the government coalition yesterday 
was not to negotiate the matter but to explain the problem to 
one another and to think about what to do next so that problems 
like this will not arise in the future, as well as to part 
without anger. I think we have succeeded in doing this. I 
shall stay on in the post until I am released in writing by the 
president in accordance with the Constitution. [end recording] 

</TEXT>

