<H3> <TI>   Serb Police Arrest PPK, LDK Leaders </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU1102220694 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1900 
GMT 10 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU1102220694 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana TVSH Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Albanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Kosova Information Center reports that at about 
1400 [1300 GMT] on Thursday, Serbian police arrested the 
leadership of the Kosova Parliamentary Party [PPK] in Lipjan and 
that of the Kosova Democratic Alliance [LDK] branch in this 
commune. It is reported that the chairman of the LDK branch in 
Shtimje commune was also arrested. 
  A local leader informed the Kosova Information Center that 
the PPK Central Presidency and the LDK local leadership were 
holding meetings in the offices of the LDK branch in Lipjan. 
The number and names of those arrested are still unknown. 

</TEXT>

